info.name: FAZ.net Night Mode / Nachtmodus
info.description:
A style for viewing FAZ.net at night.

Black background, grey text, dark yellow links.

Also removes some site elements that distract from reading the news. You can easily modify the source code to change this.
info.additionalInfo:
v1.00
Works great as of October 2012.

Based on the "dark blue (s²)" style for FAZ.net (which was not dark enough for my taste).

If this style removes elements that you would like to keep: simply modify the CSS, e.g. remove the first block of code completely.
